titleStmt.title: Edward T. Newell notebook on coins of Cyprus, Syria, Phoenicia, Babylon, Alexandria, and the East, undated

note.p: Notebook binder with notes on ancient coins of Cyprus, Syria, Phoenicia, Babylon, Alexandria, and the East. Includes some loose items relating to Babylon and the Euphrates, including two maps, a magazine offprint in German, and a hand-drawn sketch.

monogr.extent: circa 240 pages ; 28 x 22 cm.+ loose maps and other items.
